      • getModelSimpleExtensionGroups

        public List<Object> getModelSimpleExtensionGroups()
        Gets the value of the modelSimpleExtensionGroups property.

        This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the modelSimpleExtensionGroups property.

        For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

            getModelSimpleExtensionGroups().add(newItem);
